<h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2 leading-tight">Scrabble World Champions</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-8 not-prose">Scrabble Words Finder · English Solver · Word of the Day</p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 6 min read</p>

      <p class="lead text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Since 1991, the World Scrabble Championship has crowned the best players on Earth. From Peter Morris's inaugural win to Nigel Richards's legendary dominance, the tournament has grown into a global competition spanning dozens of countries. Here's the complete history.</p>

