      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Nigel Richards — The Greatest of All Time</h2>
      <p>Nigel Richards is widely regarded as the most dominant Scrabble player in history. Originally from New Zealand and now competing under the Malaysian flag, Richards has achieved feats no other player has matched.</p>
      <div class="border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 rounded-lg p-4 my-6">
        <p class="font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-2">Richards's Achievements</p>
