          <li>5+ World Scrabble Championship titles (English)</li>
          <li>Won the French-language World Championship without speaking French — memorised the dictionary</li>
          <li>Multiple national titles across different countries</li>
          <li>Known for photographic memory and near-perfect board vision</li>
          <li>Rarely speaks publicly, letting his play do the talking</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

