          <li>Most consecutive titles: Nigel Richards (2011, 2013)</li>
          <li>First non-English-speaking champion: Sujjayakorn (Thailand, 2003)</li>
          <li>The 2015 French WSC win by Richards stunned the Scrabble world</li>
        </ul>
